Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陌生的景象 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你不喜欢和敌人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 这里就是火星圈最大的卫星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二月球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是那些被遗忘者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀着坚强的信念 建起的维甘的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我力求建立最强大的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论技术 士气 军队向心力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无一不是顶级水准
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群被遗忘在火星的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何能拥有这样的军事力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会负责收押俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他暂时留在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身份略显特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在EXA-DB中搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对设计制造新型高达有帮助的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人告诉您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用维甘的最新技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设计制造新型高达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊泽尔坎特大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达也是能凭空造出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EXA-DB 实在超乎想象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那是旧国家战争时代的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被禁止的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争本身虽然愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科技却会因此迅猛发展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说在那个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是一台最普通的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也远非现在可比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一位机师 则可以同时操纵几百台部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至驾驶集战争技术于一身的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大规模杀伤性武器横行战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发现的还只是其中的极小一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 正是这部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成了维甘的现代技术基础
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦获得全部技术遗产会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以实现的话 这场战争就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会宣告结束吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天佑我维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被诅咒的秘宝 EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里就可以 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你就是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在地球圈抓到的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这孩子难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的眼神对你没有任何好处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一声令下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几秒钟后 你就会成为一具死尸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底打算带我来这里干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于张口说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会作为地球圈的代表见证这里的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见证维甘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过今天旅途劳顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经为你准备了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责照顾你 请叫我玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 所以才会被允许使用这间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这张脸 简直像极了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊泽尔坎特大人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说好久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪会给你特别待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:08:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则俘虏一般住不上这样的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 把身上的衣服脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换新衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要带我上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们为何要向地球联邦发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中的真正原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了侵略地球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵略地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是侵略 而是夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发誓不惜任何手段要重返地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并夺回作为人的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论有什么理由都不能这么做！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能够体会到吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被宣告「死刑」的人们的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「火星圈」「梦想中的新天地」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那不过都是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败的星球改造和磁力风暴所引发的不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使那里沦为一片死病蔓延之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星圈的人们在与病魔的斗争中繁衍生息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,编织起了属于他们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一天要重返地球家园！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这个心愿深埋心中 生存了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们选择战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为夺回这片名为地球的故土
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们战斗的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能够体会到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 就算这样 维甘也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ID卡和联络用终端
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以在城市中和我们取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者购买必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是你的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心 过后会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 去了解一下维甘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去亲眼看看自己恨之入骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人真正的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有丑话说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你时刻受到监视
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做无谓的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过多少次了 不要再干这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这里的人吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没用 不过就是点擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我家 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是小心点为好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家活得都挺难的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被逼得走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去床上躺着！露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我叫吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我叫露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不过没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫狄恩 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 一起吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想听听外面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧是从哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有点…远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的学校 教些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧擅长什么体育项目？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕吉欧 我也好想去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聊聊天 有时还吵嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一定很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没上过学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道 这种病需要卧床
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少年是高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不应该审讯他 从他嘴里收集情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 时不我待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有我的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说吧 你们那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是问你 你们卫星上的病情控制怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想说的话 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经 活不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多还有三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太不公平了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹她做错了什么非要死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的病 这么重吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以想想办法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便有药 也不可能照顾到我们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不可能完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是多活一段时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球上的家伙们在安全的地方享福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们却被迫过着这种生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太自私了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会把我们带回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有 看到妹妹那么开心过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好不要再来找我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她来说 只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不可以来找我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己的身体 自己最清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露乌！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看看更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看看更多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算去更多的地方 认识更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离别马上就会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会徒增伤感…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得害怕迎接死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁愿那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁愿最后变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想活得像个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想活得像个人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想和吉欧聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多事想问吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲眼见证火星圈的现状后有何感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们总是为心爱的人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望从家庭中获得温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在这里 如此单纯的愿望也会遭到践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的人们因害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而刻意压制着感情生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 狄恩他们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你遇到的那个少年的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实大家小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都保留有一份人类的感性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 随着长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便失去了那份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不再执着于家人和恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕全心全意的去爱别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们因为不愿被夺走情感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而发出的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并非为死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为不能活得像个正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而伤心欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一场简单的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在之前的每一次战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都为你们提供了幸存的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对那些浑浑噩噩的地球种们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我始终都在向他们发问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否有生存的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否有生存的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法理解！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人对那位少年太缺乏戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是个孩子 毕竟是敌人的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得放松监视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如有万一 由我们亲手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要那个少年的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 今天我又把那孩子错看成了罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是命运的捉弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诊断如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说了 剩余时间不足六个月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要亲手打开通往伊甸的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这是我们活到今天的目的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从失去罗米的那天开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离别马上就会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会变得害怕迎接死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁愿那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁愿最后变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想活得像个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想活得像个人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并非为死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为不能活得像个正常人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而伤心欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们捕获高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功阻止了联邦增强战斗力的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸计划开始进入最终阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为这一天赌上了全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次告诉你这项计划的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下从未有一天忘记过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为夺回作为人的尊严和权利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这份崇高的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指引我战斗到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待你的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 马上进入零部件的高速成型工序
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生自维甘的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的高达
